{"tid":1817422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 1.11 連儂活動手足 必讀","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T03:15:45.000Z","uid":218313,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c42709d6463b17c18f690a25314454c4a9f99aae","tid":1817422,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"TLDW<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有關1.11 全城連儂活動:<br />\n<br />\n1&gt; 近幾日連儂牆有組織除去, 街上面大部份SLOGAN 都油左油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2&gt; 明顯港共想盡快將運動痕跡係城巿消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3&gt; 燉炳強上任後, 連和理非都已經成為尻捉目標, 有理由相信佢地想<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">捉埋活躍既連儂文宣組</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4&gt; 捉左呢班文宣, 想阻嚇和理非貼連儂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n1&gt; <strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔係話叫你地唔好去1.11 全城連儂</span></ins></strong>, 但必須要有心理準備會尻捉, 要提高警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2&gt; 哨兵都要小心, 唔好單拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>只要有人有紙, <ins>全城都係連儂</ins>, 唔需要做埋預告去邊度貼架!</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同我將全香港變晒連儂!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足萬事小心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申: 單拖文宣步兵</span></span>"},{"pid":"f11dade8374ca6c7e73b3dac52afbad1f5f6a99e","tid":1817422,"uid":50094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"手足你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，小弟整左個網叫 EventVote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkeventvote.com/overview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeventvote.com%2Foverview&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF06zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=5ed0ca19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkeventvote.com/overview</a><br />\n<br />\n《最集中最方便既活動資訊平台-HKEventVote》<br />\nlihkg link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1817084/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1817084/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n想大家有個免費平台share 唔同嘅活動📣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭日程又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聯署又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約一班手足去懲罰黃店都好<br />\n<br />\n網站前期冇人用冇乜event<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要麻煩大家係入面開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要你search 時間，地區，類型，就可以搵到適合你既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e12c9155cc8d6928ff582136ac2505320011749","tid":1817422,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"509c4edc6c89927b7fd2e906b11e3934e0413262","tid":1817422,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike